                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/145825573/">一二三</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-03-24</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">革命像旋风 又像齿轮</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1151250249">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1151250249" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1151250249" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1151250249">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/121718178/">孔默</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2017-02-12</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">大学猎奇时所阅，尽管政治立场和十七年文学截然相反，但调调却差不多（善于抹黑对方，且抹黑的触目惊心）。但就小说艺术而言，不算太差。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1121185749">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1121185749" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1121185749" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1121185749">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/73714750/">妖怪瓶</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2016-12-14</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">也只是一个特例而已。而且小说家言，除了宣传和惑人心外没有什么杀伤力的。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1110454699">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1110454699" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1110454699" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1110454699">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/54704732/">剥洋葱</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2017-06-27</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">旋风，这个名字取得太好。思路挺深刻，“小说”写得太烂。曲笔不会用，直言无隐，一定写不好小说。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

